<paragraph id="B44B8D79FFB4FFF7FF15B3D0FA95F8E6" blockId="8.[136,1451,1651,1854]" pageId="8" pageNumber="137">
Notes:â€” 
<taxonomicName id="73F4F6FAFFB4FFF7FF42B3D0FE7CF92D" authorityName="Schischkin" authorityYear="1961" box="[223,482,1760,1781]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Senecio" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="8" pageNumber="137" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="series" series="Racemuliferae">
<emphasis id="8680516BFFB4FFF7FF42B3D0FEB4F92D" box="[223,298,1760,1781]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="137">Senecio</emphasis>
ser. 
<emphasis id="8680516BFFB4FFF7FECBB3D0FE7CF92D" box="[342,482,1760,1781]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="137">Racemuliferae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
includes a single species, i.e. 
<taxonomicName id="73F4F6FAFFB4FFF7FC9CB3D0FC17F92D" authorityName="Pavlov, MZ" authorityYear="1950" box="[769,905,1760,1781]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Senecio" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="8" pageNumber="137" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="racemulifer">
<emphasis id="8680516BFFB4FFF7FC9CB3D0FC17F92D" box="[769,905,1760,1781]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="137">S. racemulifer</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(= 
<taxonomicName id="73F4F6FAFFB4FFF7FC37B3D0FB16F92D" box="[938,1160,1760,1781]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Jacobaea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="8" pageNumber="137" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="racemulifera">
<emphasis id="8680516BFFB4FFF7FC37B3D0FB16F92D" box="[938,1160,1760,1781]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="137">Jacobaea racemulifera</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
). No infrageneric division has been previously made in the genus 
<taxonomicName id="73F4F6FAFFB4FFF7FD90B234FDF7F8C1" authorityName="Miller" authorityYear="1754" box="[525,617,1796,1817]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Jacobaea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="8" pageNumber="137" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="8680516BFFB4FFF7FD90B234FDF7F8C1" box="[525,617,1796,1817]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="137">Jacobaea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, so at this stage it seems more reasonable to directly reduce 
<emphasis id="8680516BFFB4FFF7FB3AB234FB24F8C1" box="[1191,1210,1796,1817]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="137">
<collectionCode id="D2E515BCFFB4FFF7FB3AB234FB28F8C1" box="[1191,1206,1796,1817]" country="Sweden" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:15668" name="Department of Botany, Swedish Museum of Natural History" pageId="8" pageNumber="137" type="Herbarium">S</collectionCode>
.
</emphasis>
ser. 
<emphasis id="8680516BFFB4FFF7FB79B234FAEEF8C1" box="[1252,1392,1796,1817]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="137">Racemuliferae</emphasis>
to the synonymy of 
<taxonomicName id="73F4F6FAFFB4FFF7FEDCB218FE03F8E5" authorityName="Miller" authorityYear="1754" box="[321,413,1832,1853]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Jacobaea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="8" pageNumber="137" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="8680516BFFB4FFF7FEDCB218FE03F8E5" box="[321,413,1832,1853]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="137">Jacobaea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
than to transfer it to the genus as a series or section to avoid making any new combination.
</paragraph>
